title: Dr Richard Schulze - Save your Life Interviews
description:
Dr Richard Schulze - Save your Life Interviews

FLV files downloaded from Google Video before videos were removed from Google Video.

Download, Watch, Seed, Copy and give to your friends and Family.

Dr Richard Schulze spent 20 years treating people who were diagnosed with supposedly "Incurable Diseases" who had been given Death Sentences by their doctors, only to have most of his patients get well and then go on to outlive their doctors.

The information in these videos could save your Life and the Life of a loved one.	

FLV Player can be downloaded here to watch videos ==> http://www.martijndevisser.com/blog/flv-player/
